narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Quinault Indian Nation is a Clinic/Center  Rehabilitation  Substance Use Disorder provider based in Aberdeen, WA. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $39.2M in Medicaid payments across 153K claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: At $39.2M in Medicaid payments, this provider represents significant public healthcare spending. Understanding where these dollars go helps ensure the program serves those who need it most.
